Websocket API is used for interactive 2 way communication session between browser and server.
Sends message to  the server and receive event based responses without having to poll the server for a response.

WebSockets are good way to handle high-scale data transfer between server-client.

Websockets are bidirectional

Websockets are statefull protocols, connection between client and server stays alive until terminated by one of the parties.

Real Life Example:  Stock Trading Application
Game Application requiring changes in UI
Chatting Application
